"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "46ddbb77fb9bd746b489700c00b49b466763ae1d3e5eaf0a13d8eb7f7573d0c3"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-03-16T20:50:42.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Verdier for over 260 millioner kroner gikk tapt i hyttebranner i 2015. N\u00e5 h\u00e5per Kjetil Monkvik i Tr\u00f8ndelag brann- og redningstjeneste at flere sjekker r\u00f8ykvarsleren neste gang de drar p\u00e5 hytta."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/article12286177.ece/c6gcvq/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Montasje_hytter%C3%B8yk%20(2).jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/3a32a0bf42391f198c0d075ea24f9b0803aabcb8.jpg?58d4392c"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["4 av 10 sjekker ikke r\u00f8ykvarsleren p\u00e5 hytta -adressa.no", "- Ikke ta un\u00f8dige sjanser", "- Vit hvor du er", "- Skumapparater kan fryse", "P\u00e5budt \u00e5 feie pipe og ildsted"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "3a32a0bf42391f198c0d075ea24f9b0803aabcb8"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["p\u00e5ske", "Brann", "Hytte"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "p\u00e5ske,Brann,Hytte"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["r\u00f8ykvarsler", "sjekker r\u00f8ykvarsleren", "hytta"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "statens"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "tr\u00f8ndelag"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "kjetil monkvik"}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negative"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/innenriks"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/article12286177.ece/c6gcvq/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Montasje_hytter%C3%B8yk%20(2).jpg"},